<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <%- include('partials/head', { seo }) %>
</head>
<body>
  <%- include('partials/header') %>

  <main>
    <section class="hero hero--subtle">
      <div class="container">
        <div class="hero-content">
          <nav aria-label="Breadcrumb" class="breadcrumb"><ol><li><a href="/">Home</a></li><li aria-current="page">About</li></ol></nav>
          <span class="eyebrow">Our story</span>
          <h1>Building Bhojan Mitra with restaurateurs from day zero</h1>
          <p>Bhojan Mitra is developed by Aarohita Vigyan — a team obsessed with blending AI, IoT, and hospitality. We are working alongside founding partners to craft a voice-led POS platform that feels natural for Indian restaurants.</p>
          <div class="hero-actions">
            <a href="/contact" class="btn btn-primary btn-lg">Talk to the founders</a>
            <a href="#team" class="btn btn-outline btn-lg">Meet the team</a>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section id="mission" class="features">
      <div class="container">
        <span class="eyebrow">Mission</span>
        <h2>Why we are building a voice-first POS</h2>
        <div class="features-grid">
          <div class="feature-card">
            <h3>Hospitality rooted</h3>
            <p>We’ve spent years on the restaurant floor. Every workflow, report, and automation is co-designed with operators to reduce training and chaos.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="feature-card">
            <h3>Voice + IoT future</h3>
            <p>We believe ordering will be conversational and devices should follow along. Bhojan Mitra orchestrates printers, displays, and mobile surfaces automatically.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="feature-card">
            <h3>Radical transparency</h3>
            <p>Founding partners see the roadmap, sprint plans, and pricing in the open. We grow only when restaurants get measurable value.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section id="team" class="ecosystem">
      <div class="container">
        <span class="eyebrow">Team</span>
        <h2>The founders behind Bhojan Mitra</h2>
        <div class="founder-card">
          <!-- Photo -->
          <div class="founder-photo-col">
            <div class="founder-photo-wrap">
              <img src="/images/Screenshot 2026-04-13 164408.png" alt="Kunwar Kanhaiya Kamlakant Pandey" class="founder-photo">
            </div>
            <p class="founder-role">CEO &amp; Founder</p>
            <p class="founder-name">Kunwar Kanhaiya Kamlakant Pandey</p>
          </div>

          <!-- Bio -->
          <div class="founder-bio-col">
            <h3 class="founder-bio-heading">Bio</h3>
            <p>Kunwar Kanhaiya Pandey is a technology-driven founder specializing in AI, IoT, and intelligent automation systems. He has built and led multiple tech initiatives focused on solving operational inefficiencies through applied AI.</p>
            <p>As the founder of Bhojan Mitra, Kunwar identified a critical gap in the restaurant industry—where manual workflows, language diversity, and staffing constraints limit scalability. His solution integrates voice recognition, automation, and real-time data to modernize restaurant operations without increasing complexity.</p>

            <h3 class="founder-bio-heading">Let's Connect</h3>
            <div class="founder-socials">
              <a href="https://wa.me/91" class="founder-social-link" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" aria-label="WhatsApp">
                <img src="/images/footer-whatsapp.svg" alt="WhatsApp" width="36" height="36">
              </a>
              <a href="https://x.com" class="founder-social-link" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" aria-label="X / Twitter">
                <svg width="36" height="36" viewBox="0 0 36 36" fill="none"><rect width="36" height="36" rx="8" fill="#000"/><path d="M20.18 16.77L27.1 9h-1.63l-5.99 6.77L14.5 9H9l7.27 10.25L9 27h1.63l6.36-7.19L22.5 27H28L20.18 16.77zm-2.25 2.54l-.74-1.03L11.2 10.2h2.52l4.73 6.58.74 1.03 6.14 8.54h-2.52l-5.08-7.04z" fill="#fff"/></svg>
              </a>
              <a href="https://instagram.com" class="founder-social-link" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" aria-label="Instagram">
                <img src="/images/footer-instagram.svg" alt="Instagram" width="36" height="36">
              </a>
              <a href="https://linkedin.com" class="founder-social-link" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" aria-label="LinkedIn">
                <svg width="36" height="36" viewBox="0 0 36 36" fill="none"><rect width="36" height="36" rx="8" fill="#0A66C2"/><path d="M13 14h-3v10h3V14zm-1.5-4.5A1.75 1.75 0 1110 11.25 1.75 1.75 0 0111.5 9.5zM26 18.5c0-2.5-1.3-4.5-3.7-4.5-1.1 0-2.1.6-2.6 1.5V14h-3v10h3v-5.2c0-1.3.7-2.3 1.9-2.3 1.1 0 1.9.8 1.9 2.3V24h3v-5.5z" fill="#fff"/></svg>
              </a>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="cta-section">
      <div class="container">
        <h2>We’d love to collaborate with you</h2>
        <p>Tell us about your operation and we’ll share how the pilot cohort works.</p>
        <div class="hero-actions center">
          <a href="https://billing.aarohitavigyan.com" class="btn btn-primary btn-lg">Apply for the pilot</a>
          <a href="/business-plan" class="btn btn-secondary btn-lg">View investor brief</a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>
  </main>

  <%- include('partials/footer') %>
  <script src="/js/main.js"></script>
</body>
</html>
